{"tid":812163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】網民熱話：港人日本機場打尖　拍片者同被公審","createTime":"2018-09-09T12:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T13:17:56.000Z","uid":202698,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7dcbc21c43aa5290f839178ea66b535374264a","tid":812163,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/201107_39d9cb0dace0aa455085a9d02b24510d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F201107_39d9cb0dace0aa455085a9d02b24510d.jpg&h=defac678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909154340396-0909_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180909%2Fbkn-20180909154340396-0909_00822_001.html&d=QGBZOjw%2BBRCrEOsp%2FpguYhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1ef062b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909154340396-0909_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKDiscussForum/videos/2185419175038991/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKDiscussForum%2Fvideos%2F2185419175038991%2F&d=QGBZOjw%2BBRCrEOsp%2FpguYhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d3708bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKDiscussForum/videos/2185419175038991/</a><br />\n<br />\n港人「醜」出國際事件時有所聞，日前大阪受風災影響，不少旅客萌生「思鄉」之情，希望盡早登機離開日本。在人多擠迫的環境，難免會出現爭執。<span style=\"color: red;\">昨日（8日）有網民在Facebook群組「onX仔女同盟會 (onX限定)」 貼文並上載影片，怒斥一對港人情侶在機場進行安全檢查時打尖。不過，有網民看過片段後反而認為，拍片者亦同樣影衰港人。</span><br />\n<br />\n在19秒的影片中，拍片者不斷用粗口質問對方：<span style=\"color: red;\">「打乜X嘢尖」？更謂：「我就擺你上網！」</span>爭吵聲引來其他旅客的奇異目光。與男友同行的女事主回應指：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我依家咪去排番隊囉」</span>，而男方則一臉無奈地表示：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我問清楚啫，唔係打你尖」</span>。惟鏡頭外的另一把女聲繼續不滿：「你哋仲理直氣壯咁」。網民Hunter Ku在發文時，留言謂：「自己唔啱在先，仲撩人隻揪，好多台灣人同日本人望住晒，真係影衰晒香港人。」<br />\n<br />\n影片在網上廣泛流傳，有網民不值打尖者所為，不過拍片者卻未有得到多數網民的支持。不少人認為拍片者言談間太多粗口，「一樣影衰香港人」，「講粗口同埋拍人片又好啱？」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打尖者唔啱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍片者唔啱"},{"pid":"8ddd5292a5f06695670d037d683fa4092f63e654","tid":812163,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"香港人只係一班識講廣東話既大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6740b0b1193f4dd7ba6fd3d4005c6853583159","tid":812163,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"肯定係大陸仔"},{"pid":"c0c58bd86eac3d6ebddb11fa38fa314a4b3832d2","tid":812163,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"呢d係咪就係「香港民族」？定廣支那種扮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b6fddb11eca6237322b04b6c789fef4eeaf90e","tid":812163,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"奶支奶得多, 人都變埋支那人"},{"pid":"90478f3e9e8244025ce943a3979af096cadcd1a1","tid":812163,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲係自己人犯錯<br />\n就會<strong>搵位入批評者轉移視線</strong><br />\n<br />\n拍片者係白人咪屈人針對華人<br />\n今次批評者講粗口就自覺有位入"},{"pid":"2ed2dd81a87a16c6516f451074918890a6e7d7e6","tid":812163,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"拍片條友未講點解覺得佢係打尖<br />\n<br />\n請勿跟車太貼"},{"pid":"db9dbc67a9661a4035d1ebcdba80c14cbb4c3663","tid":812163,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"等於5毛屌本土派都係針對人講粗口, 咩唔尊重<br />\n<br />\n完全無料反駁本土主張<br />\n<br />\n咩9野唔好比位人入完全係ON9"},{"pid":"8791bb9ecbad003a414af49b6f574818436f984d","tid":812163,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"求奇啦安檢"